<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2019-06-03</DATELINE><TITLE>A Comprehensive Analytical Framework for Risks, Disasters and Crises</TITLE><BODY>Early warning and emergency management is a comprehensive and integrated system that deals with all sorts of emergencies, risks and crises, and involves various sectors of society and government departments. A consistent and holistic approach, however, has previously been lacking in both research and practice.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>